<h3>Stage 4: Mature/Declining (Sales slowing)</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Opportunity:</strong> Clearance sales, deep discounts</li>
<li><strong>Risk:</strong> Being replaced by newer versions</li>
<li><strong>Strategy:</strong> Great for bargain hunters, not for resellers</li>
</ul>

<h2>Red Flags: Fake Bestsellers to Avoid</h2>

<h3>Warning Signs of Inflated Sales:</h3>

<ul>
<li>❌ Perfect 5.0 rating with thousands of sales (suspiciously perfect)</li>
<li>❌ Generic reviews ("Good product", "Fast shipping") without details</li>
<li>❌ All reviews posted on same dates (bulk fake reviews)</li>
<li>❌ No customer photos in reviews (real buyers share photos)</li>
<li>❌ Seller has multiple identical shops (review manipulation)</li>
<li>❌ Price too good to be true compared to similar items</li>
<li>❌ Stock photos only, no original photography</li>
<li>❌ Vague product descriptions without specifications</li>
</ul>

<h3>How to Verify Authenticity:</h3>

<ul>
<li>✅ Read 3-star reviews (most honest feedback)</li>
<li>✅ Check seller's other products (consistent quality?)</li>
<li>✅ Look at review dates (spread over time or clustered?)</li>
<li>✅ Verify with Q&A section (active seller engagement?)</li>
<li>✅ Check if product exists on other platforms</li>
</ul>

